Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:18.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:23.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:26.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:33.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:44.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:59.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:03.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eighteen million years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:29.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Earth was inhabited by a\Ncreature called the trilobite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:38.12,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,170.389)}Reborn Fossil
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:38.12,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,670.389)}The Blood-Sucking Trilobite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:44.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shimura is hard at work\Ntrying to find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:47.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to restore this ancient creature\Nfrom its fossilized form.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:55.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But can the trilobite be awakened\Nfrom its 18 million year slumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked. I've finally done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for that experiment\Nto bear fruit for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to combine that ancient organism
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with a cyborg that drinks\Nhuman blood to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and send this new monster\Nout into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This will further our plans\Nfor world conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Name the trilobite cyborg Zanbronzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish the human's modifications\Nby 6:00 tomorrow evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then perform the blood swap with\Nthe trilobite at 2:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out on my overnight hike now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Take care, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too rambunctious, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And Papa, I bet you'll get\Nto do a lot of research
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with me out of your hair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid's got my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All who stand in the way of\Nour world conquest are enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your duty, as the chosen one,\Nto kill those enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where it could have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't have been\Nable to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here\Nto take the trilobite away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the blood transfusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Inhabitants of a world\Nyou know nothing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave, or I'll call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take you somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this appear\Nunderneath my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Doctor Shimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you must feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget that\Nyou've been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A trilobite fossil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want your help to\Nbring it back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring peace to all of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar. I refuse to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in no position\Nto refuse, Doctor Shimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or we'll have this\Ntrilobite suck your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous. Trilobites can't\Ndrink human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's been the scientific\Nconsensus up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've used our science\Nto break through that barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared to be test subject one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How... How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimura! It's time to drop\Nthat idealism of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? I want your answer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... begin the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:48.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plan was to create a monster\Nthat grew as it drank human blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,use it to throw humanity into chaos,\Nand thus conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Additionally, their first targets\Nwould be the Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:57.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and FBI agent Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I read something in a book yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It said there's a doctor working\Nto bring ancient creatures back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancient creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you adults need\Nmore fantasy in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The best you can manage is sinking\N15 years' pay on a new dream house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You gross litterbug!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You could learn something from kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seventeen-Article Constitution says...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that creepy bug...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... the Racing Club, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No husband until I'm 30, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.79,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}Tachibana Racing Club
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We failed in our plan\Nto attack FBI scum Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put Plan B\Ninto operation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This one says I'll get a date next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Drain her! Drain her dry, Zanbronzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:12.46,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}Tachibana Auto Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You damned monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari! Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hold out on us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Agree to work with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll restore your\Nwife to good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, Wataru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These scales might be\Nthe key to solving all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, look after Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the university lab\Nto investigate these scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider doesn't realize I've shrunk myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:38.32,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's nasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All that garlic is enough\Nto drive a man mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But it keeps vampires away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Shocker for doing this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop thinking it\Nwhen I was looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd things go at the university?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it might be an Earth\Norganism that went extinct long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's like that thing I read...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... there's a guy named Doctor Shimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing research to bring ancient\Norganisms back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shimura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you've agreed\Nto help us, Doctor Shimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have your word, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't harm Wataru.\NYou have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome your visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to draw suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget that\NI'm standing right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalling won't get me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was hoping you'd\Nshow me your trilobites.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid you're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The laboratory at Johoku University\Nwanted them back, and took them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, have a seat.\N- Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking a bit\Ngreen around the gills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strange. There's somebody\Nelse in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is somebody after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:08.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,Is somebody after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there's a Shocker monster\Nbehind these curtains,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it could spell tragedy\Nfor this household...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's not here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru... say hello to our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Doctor Shimura's trilobites\Nare involved in this somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Johoku University laboratory\Nsaid they never asked for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then someone stole them from the doctor,\Nand then threatened him not to tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Change of circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop dragging your feet and get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shimura, it seems your\Npart is done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to experience\NZanbronzo's blood-sucking for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a fool, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I shortened the trilobite's lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means you'll need\Nme again very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I must protect my family and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can discuss the rest after\Nyou restore my wife to good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the plan to the next stage\Nbefore the Kamen Rider arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the kid around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fast, I'll give them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is. The way into Shocker's base!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. It's a time bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. They planned for\Nthe fact that we might escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. Where has he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneda. With the trilobites\NI restored to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Shocker... they're going\Nto send them all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're absolutely inhuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. You handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:19.49,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2F30D2&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs60}Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that bag this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Zanbronzo drink your\Nblood and send it to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, watch out for that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting weaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor... he did something to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, time for my last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you right, Zanbronzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He was a fearsome opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my end...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning to my original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The antidote that Doctor Shimura\Ncreated seems to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then... Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:22:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish Ichimonji could have joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an odd one, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets uncomfortable\Nin cheerful settings like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's just very bashful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, why don't we have another\Ntoast, to Mr. Ichimonji's health?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fine idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's have another toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:33.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato saved everyone\Nfrom the blood-sucking monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.69,0:23:35.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But what will he\Nbe forced to face next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't lose, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.71,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.23,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:45.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the ant-eating devil Arigabari.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:50.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Arigabari seeks to use a deadly bacteria\Nknown as "The Curse of the Amazon"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:51.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to conquer Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:55.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato picks up on their\Nscheme and heads for Shocker's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:56.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:01.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Deathmatch! The Ant-Eating\NDevil Arigabari."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:01.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\fscy90)\bord1\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)\3c&H000000&}Deathmatch! The Ant-Eating\NDevil Arigabari."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:10.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:13.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:15.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:18.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:22.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:24.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.47,0:24:25.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:28.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:34.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:37.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.61,0:24:41.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:45.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Reborn Fossil: The Blood-Sucking Trilobite